title: Viking 5-Ply Professional Cookware Collection
description:
Our signature Viking 5-Ply Professional Cookware is fully bonded and constructed to ensure responsive even heating and easy maintenance.  Handcrafted in the USA.

Three distinct layers of aluminum create a solid core that is sandwiched between layers of stainless steel to deliver even heat throughout the bottom and sides of the pan for consistent results whether sautéing, searing, or frying.
